      <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#d2a4b3bba1babcb3a4bbb0b3bcb5b7a0b3e0e092b5bfb3bbbefcb1bdbf" class="contact-item">✉️ <span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="2650474f554e4847504f44474841435447141466414b474f4a0845494b">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/vaishnavi-bangera-27506229b/" target="_blank" class="contact-item">🔗 LinkedIn</a>
